---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sobre Nosotros - LEAR" description="Conoce más sobre LEAR, nuestros valores y misión">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-lear-primary via-lear-primary-light to-lear-secondary text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-10 w-80 h-80 bg-lear-secondary rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-10 w-96 h-96 bg-lear-accent rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-white/20">
        <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-lear-secondary rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
        SOBRE NOSOTROS
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black mb-4">Nuestra historia y propósito</h1>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/90 max-w-2xl">
        Conoce el camino que nos trajo hasta aquí y lo que nos impulsa cada día.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-lear-gray-900 mb-6">Nuestra Historia</h2>
        <p class="text-lear-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          LEAR nace con la visión de ofrecer servicios integrales de fisioterapia y rehabilitación
          de la más alta calidad. Antes conocidos como Fisio con Elena, hemos evolucionado para
          convertirnos en un centro integral que combina la experiencia profesional con un enfoque
          personalizado en cada tratamiento.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lear-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Nuestro compromiso es proporcionar a cada paciente las herramientas y el acompañamiento
          necesario para alcanzar sus objetivos de salud y bienestar, ya sea recuperándose de una
          lesión, mejorando su condición física o buscando prevenir futuras complicaciones.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-lear-bg-primary">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Mission -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="inline-block p-3 bg-lear-primary/10 rounded-lg mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lear-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-lear-gray-900 mb-4">Nuestra Misión</h2>
          <p class="text-lear-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Proporcionar servicios de fisioterapia y rehabilitación de excelencia, utilizando
            técnicas actualizadas y un enfoque personalizado que priorice el bienestar integral
            de cada paciente, ayudándoles a alcanzar sus objetivos de salud y calidad de vida.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Vision -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="inline-block p-3 bg-lear-secondary/10 rounded-lg mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lear-secondary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-lear-gray-900 mb-4">Nuestra Visión</h2>
          <p class="text-lear-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Ser reconocidos como un centro de referencia en fisioterapia y rehabilitación integral,
            destacándonos por nuestro profesionalismo, innovación en tratamientos y el compromiso
            genuino con la recuperación y bienestar de nuestros pacientes.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-lear-gray-900 mb-4">
          Nuestros Valores
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-lear-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Los principios que guían nuestro trabajo diario.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
        <!-- Value 1 -->
        <div class="text-center bg-lear-bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-md border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="inline-block p-4 bg-lear-primary/10 rounded-full mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lear-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4.318 6.318a4.5 4.5 0 000 6.364L12 20.364l7.682-7.682a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364L12 7.636l-1.318-1.318a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-lear-gray-900 mb-2">Compromiso</h3>
          <p class="text-lear-gray-600">
            Dedicación total a la recuperación y bienestar de nuestros pacientes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 2 -->
        <div class="text-center bg-lear-bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-md border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="inline-block p-4 bg-lear-primary/10 rounded-full mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lear-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-lear-gray-900 mb-2">Profesionalismo</h3>
          <p class="text-lear-gray-600">
            Excelencia en cada tratamiento y atención brindada.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 3 -->
        <div class="text-center bg-lear-bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-md border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="inline-block p-4 bg-lear-primary/10 rounded-full mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lear-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-lear-gray-900 mb-2">Personalización</h3>
          <p class="text-lear-gray-600">
            Tratamientos adaptados a las necesidades únicas de cada persona.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Value 4 -->
        <div class="text-center bg-lear-bg-primary rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-md border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="inline-block p-4 bg-lear-primary/10 rounded-full mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-lear-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-lear-gray-900 mb-2">Innovación</h3>
          <p class="text-lear-gray-600">
            Actualización constante con las mejores prácticas y técnicas.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-lear-bg-primary to-lear-bg-secondary">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-lear-gray-900 mb-4">
          ¿Qué nos hace diferentes?
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="p-2 bg-lear-primary/10 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-lear-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lear-gray-900 mb-2">Enfoque Integral</h3>
              <p class="text-lear-gray-600">
                No solo tratamos síntomas, abordamos la causa raíz del problema para una recuperación completa y duradera.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="p-2 bg-lear-primary/10 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-lear-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lear-gray-900 mb-2">Atención Personalizada</h3>
              <p class="text-lear-gray-600">
                Cada paciente recibe un plan de tratamiento diseñado específicamente para sus necesidades y objetivos.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-md border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <div class="p-2 bg-lear-primary/10 rounded-lg">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-lear-primary" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-lear-gray-900 mb-2">Equipo Multidisciplinario</h3>
              <p class="text-lear-gray-600">
                Combinamos la experiencia de fisioterapeutas y entrenadores personales para un servicio completo.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location & Hours Section -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-lear-bg-primary/50 to-lear-bg-secondary/30"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-lear-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-lear-secondary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-lear-primary/10 to-lear-secondary/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full font-semibold text-sm mb-6 border border-lear-primary/20">
          <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-lear-primary rounded-full animate-pulse"></div>
          VISÍTANOS
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-lear-gray-900 mb-4">
          Horario y <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-lear-primary to-lear-secondary bg-clip-text text-transparent">Ubicación</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-lear-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Estamos aquí para recibirte en nuestro centro
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Horario -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-lear-primary to-lear-secondary rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-lear-gray-900">Horario de Atención</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between py-3 border-b border-lear-gray-100">
              <span class="font-semibold text-lear-gray-900">Martes - Viernes</span>
              <div class="text-right">
                <p class="text-lear-gray-700">10:00 am - 1:00 pm</p>
                <p class="text-lear-gray-700">2:00 pm - 7:00 pm</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between py-3">
              <span class="font-semibold text-lear-gray-900">Sábado</span>
              <p class="text-lear-gray-700">10:00 am - 5:00 pm</p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-6 pt-6 border-t border-lear-gray-200">
              <p class="text-sm text-lear-gray-500 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" />
                </svg>
                Cerrado los domingos y lunes
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Ubicación -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl border border-lear-gray-100">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-lear-secondary to-lear-accent rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-lear-gray-900">Nuestra Ubicación</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <p class="text-lear-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <span class="font-semibold text-lear-gray-900">Av. Juarez 368</span><br/>
                Primero de Cobián Centro<br/>
                27000 Torreón, Coah.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="pt-4">
              <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-lear-gray-200">
                <iframe
                  src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3600.003494366944!2d-103.44710772374648!3d25.538260517800364!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x868fdbdc319ac29d%3A0xb57555f99e1e4ed5!2sAv.%20Juarez%20368%2C%20Primero%20de%20Cobi%C3%A1n%20Centro%2C%2027000%20Torre%C3%B3n%2C%20Coah.!5e0!3m2!1sen!2smx!4v1764402168552!5m2!1sen!2smx"
                  width="100%"
                  height="300"
                  style="border:0;"
                  allowfullscreen=""
                  loading="lazy"
                  referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
                  class="w-full"
                ></iframe>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-lear-gray-500 mt-3 text-center">
                Haz clic en el mapa para abrir en Google Maps
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="relative py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-lear-primary via-lear-primary-dark to-lear-secondary text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-lear-secondary rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-80 h-80 bg-lear-accent rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
        ¿Quieres ser parte de nuestra historia de éxito?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-white/90 mb-8">
        Visítanos o contáctanos para comenzar tu camino hacia una mejor salud.
      </p>
      <div class="inline-flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/20">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 bg-white/20 rounded-xl">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
          </svg>
          <span class="font-medium">Información de contacto próximamente</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
